messages.message:
Hey team, did we discontinue the visual capabilities for Converse?
cc: @fernando.piazza.ctr
No, it's still available. Can you provide more context on why you think it's discontinued?

@lydia Because I'm not able to activate the vision capabilities, despite having Research mode and the feature flag switched on (see Screenshots).

On MT AI Hub  (https://aihub.instabase.com/converse/01948e01-346e-7dec-8c75-bdc57cbaaf04)the query actually times out eventually.

This is both for UAT and for MT AI Hub Prod. However, on UAT the feature flag was removed completely, while on MT AI Hub it's still available as 'External Preview'.

The original goal of my testing was to see if the visual model could compare signatures in Converse.
